title: God of War III : Remastered  (for PS Vita)
description:
Set in the realm of Greek mythology, God of War III: Remastered is the epic third and final chapter of the God of War saga. Players will again control Kratos, an ex-Spartan warrior, as he seeks revenge against Gods who have betrayed him.
 	Gameplay and Features
 	The gameplay follows Kratos as he treats through the intimidating heights of Mt. Olympus and the dark depths of Hell to seek revenge on those who have betrayed him. Armed with the iconic double-chained blades, Kratos must take on mythology’s darkest creatures while solving intricate puzzles throughout his merciless quest to destroy Olympus.
 	This Remastered edition comes with 1080p gameplay, silky smooth combat modes, and a variety of fan-oriented enhancements. The game also features fluid, life-like characters, dynamic lighting effects, robust weapon system and world-changing scenarios. Players will have the chances to join grand-scale battles with on-screen enemies and experience more interactive levels like never before.
 	Game Mode and Rating
 	This single-player, action-adventure, role-playing game is playable on the PS4 console. It comes with a PEGI 18 rating for blood and gore, intense violence, strong language and nudity and sexual content.
category: God of War III : Remastered (for PS Vita)

title: GTA V Premium Edition  (for PS Vita)
description:
Your favourite game with an open-world environment is back and this time you have much more liberty and space to wreak havoc. Rated 18 by PEGI, developed by Rockstar North and published by Rockstar Games, Grand Theft Auto V is a single-player/online multiplayer action-adventure video game for the Xbox One console. Set in the city of Los Santos, you get to roam about the hills, beaches and countryside whensoever you please in-game. There are three playable protagonists in-game who you must utilize to make money through illegal activities, they are, Trevor, Michael and Franklin.
 	In this nefarious world, you, as the player, will be confronted by meth heads, faded celebrities, ruthless gangs, bikers, hikers and many other colourful characters. You can navigate through the expanse of the virtual world on foot or in a vehicle. Most of the missions are driving/shooting gameplay oriented. A wanted system that assesses the player’s criminalistic activities decides if the law enforcement agencies should be on your tail or not. In this open world, there are numerous activities that the player can take part in, such as, tennis, golf, cycling, yoga, parachuting and much more! Activities like robbing cars, hustling and committing petty crimes are still central in this game as in the series. However, if one wishes to make big bucks then he/she can execute elaborate and lucrative heists by using all three playable characters. The Online Mode of this game is set a few months prior to GTA V's events. Furthermore, GTA Online’s Social Club offers its members access to a slew of vehicles, weaponry and much more!
category: GTA V Premium Edition (for PS Vita)
